{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Desktop Pals is the ultimate desktop companion game. The game has a wide selection of pets to chose from, and features such as game overlay; you will never have to leave your new pal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/ENG_FEATURING.gif?t=1732791352\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features several artstyles, so you can chose which one you prefer. The pets include dogs, cats, a wolf, a panda, rabbits, a hedgehog, and more. It's a real zoo in here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The pals are interactive! Each pal has a unique reaction to you petting him, and they have natural behaviour patterns, such as falling asleep or going for a walk around your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/ENG_OVERLAY.gif?t=1732791352\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Desktop Pals also works over most modern games, so you can play with your pal during those pesky down-times, like when you are waiting for your friend to join your lobby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game also features advanced customization. You can choose the pals location on your screen, his scale, his capabilities, and more! You can change the game to your liking.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732791352","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732791352","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/2e7c717e28b7f395de569f906fb7069d1f743888/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732791352","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/2e7c717e28b7f395de569f906fb7069d1f743888/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732791352","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Desktop Pals is the ultimate desktop companion game. The game has a wide selection of pets to chose from, and features such as game overlay; you will never have to leave your new pal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/ENG_FEATURING.gif?t=1732791352\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features several artstyles, so you can chose which one you prefer. The pets include dogs, cats, a wolf, a panda, rabbits, a hedgehog, and more. It's a real zoo in here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The pals are interactive! Each pal has a unique reaction to you petting him, and they have natural behaviour patterns, such as falling asleep or going for a walk around your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/ENG_OVERLAY.gif?t=1732791352\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Desktop Pals also works over most modern games, so you can play with your pal during those pesky down-times, like when you are waiting for your friend to join your lobby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game also features advanced customization. You can choose the pals location on your screen, his scale, his capabilities, and more! You can change the game to your liking.</p>","developers":["Shutterframe Studios"],"dlc":[3305560],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/header.jpg?t=1732791352","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257062082,"mp4":{"480":"ht